ARIS Database Migrations
========================

This directory contains Alembic migrations for the ARIS metadata database.

Usage:

1. Create a new migration (autogenerate):
   aris db revision --autogenerate -m "description"

2. Apply migrations:
   aris db migrate

3. Check current migration status:
   aris db status

4. Downgrade one version:
   aris db downgrade -1

5. Show migration history:
   aris db history

The migrations use the database path from ARIS configuration (default: .aris/metadata.db).

Manual migrations can be created with:
   aris db revision -m "description"

Then edit the generated file in alembic/versions/ to add upgrade/downgrade operations.
